title: Soul.Mates.AU.S01E01-E02.Web-DL.x264-JIVE
description:
Soul Mates has fun with big life questions as the twin souls of a pair of Bondi Hipsters appear throughout history and the future in a fresh blend of sketch comedy with a narrative arc.




Soul Mates - Series 1, Episode 1


A bromance for the ages, Soul Mates is the story of two kindred spirits trapped in a cycle of death and rebirth. Across four different lifetimes with no knowledge of their past lives, they are forever drawn together as mates.


Original Air Date: 23-Oct-2014




Soul Mates - Series 1 Episode 2


Mum gives Roger and Thinge their first mission... to entice a young Russell Crowe back to NZ. In other lifetimes, Rocky spots his perfect mate; Dom forages for modelling work; and Dave detests Rob's metal-morphasis.


Original Air Date: 30-Oct-2014
